Combined Lyrics: (mainly from Imran)

Aye Raah e Haq ke Sahaheedo - O the Martyrs of True pathway
Wafa ki tasveero - Pictures of loyalty faithfulness
Tumhein Watan ki Hawayeein - wind of our Country
Salaam Kehti hein - Pays you Greetings.
Aye Raah e Haq ke Sahaheedo - O the Martyrs of True pathway

Allah Hooo (Allah ...)

Laganey Aag jo aaye they -Those who came to burn 
Aashiyaaney ko - our homeland,
Wo sholey apne lahoo se -Those flames by your own Blood,
Bhujaa diye tum ne - You extinguished them
Bachaa liyaa hai yateemi se kitney phooloun ko - you saved so many flowers (Sons and Daughters) from becoming Orphans,
Suhaag kitni bahaaro'n ke rakkh liye tum ne - you saved so many (spring) Wives for being Widowed.
Tumhein Chaman ki fazaayen Salaam kehti hein - Winds of garden pay you greetings.
Aye Raah e Haq ke Sahaheedo - O the Martyrs of True pathway

Chale jo ho ge Shahadat ka Jaam pee kar tum - When had you departed by tasting the glass of martyrdom
Rasool e Paak ne Baahoun me.... - Prophet, the pure (peace be upon him) in his arms ....
 .... le liya ho ga - ...... would have been embracing you.
Ali tumhaari shujaat pe Jhuumte hon ge - Ali (R.A) would have been celebrating your valor
Hussein Paak ne Irshaad ye kiya hoga - Hussein(RA), the pure would have Said that,
Tumhein Khuda ki Razaayein  - Blessings of the Almighty
 Salaam Kehti hein -  Pay you greetings
